                   destinations. Added 5 new chaos tests (penalty bounds, controls.js read
                   stress, skin catalogue integrity, memory-leak check, script load order).")
    ("2026-04-16" "Claude Opus 4.6" "v3.0 groundwork. Astrocompass HUD for orbit mode (bow-relative
                   bearing dial, nearest-body + warp-destination markers, autopilot tag, Sun
